{"tid":947682,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"以德報怨定狠狠地報個仇","createTime":"2018-12-19T12:34:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T12:54:19.000Z","uid":227473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"483ef472ff65041f50face1eed681ae34ab5e98d","tid":947682,"uid":227473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T12:34:13.000Z","msg":"事源係咁(地點:某hall)<br />\n<br />\n一年前，條仔散咗冇耐就同佢一齊。有條八婆(當時roommate)就懶係同佢前度frd，假好人喺背後數臭我話我乘虛而入又對朋友(意指個八婆同我條仔個ex)差，又話我條仔一早出軌有心飛咗個ex 。<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n背叛我，帶頭杯葛我地，喺背後數臭我地，做埋好多小學雞小動作，好多hallmate議論紛紛，搞到我好唔開心(嗰時以為佢好人好者，都算係frd)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">到咗今日佢呢啲八婆都終於有人要</span></span></strong> <br />\n我應該以德報怨予以祝福 定係 用盡一切辦法整死條八婆<br />\n有冇人提供方法"},{"pid":"3cda3fa30174334c354747ecedd4b38b58235ebe","tid":947682,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T12:35:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3eff778ee0368ebf6b2f8193e1e3843bdc8f144b","tid":947682,"uid":227473,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3cda3fa30174334c354747ecedd4b38b58235ebe","tid":947682,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T12:35:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T12:39:08.000Z","msg":"何來啲精🤔"},{"pid":"ff38c10fb204196c96b2744fa93e325cee7a6651","tid":947682,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T12:39:41.000Z","msg":"話俾老師知"},{"pid":"dea45ac35600706136057c095ffa248fa97b9452","tid":947682,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T12:40:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"61092fbec46a845021264170f5e921d803ec67b6","tid":947682,"uid":35488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T12:42:00.000Z","msg":"以德報怨係on9仔<br />\n只有以直報怨"},{"pid":"43644f7ef955d36854e244225dbdff8e739b4df1","tid":947682,"uid":65256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T12:43:06.000Z","msg":"原句係以德